Hi Pierre: 

I attended the opening day at Abbotsford lawn bowling and talked to members about adding croquet. Also, there were the mayor and the head of parks facilities, I talked to them together with the club treasurer. 
there seems to be some interest. There is one woman there that knows you and Lorne from Victoria and she says she misses Croquet a lot. 

I left some materials with them and hopefully, they will agree to go ahead. and then we can meet with the city guy again hopefully for park board approval to use the facility. 

Too bad I did not think to make a Fraser Valley Croquet Society business card. 

Have a great day, 
Michael Kernaghan 



